---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const images = {
  hero: "/assets/pl-hero.png",
  vision: "/assets/pl-vision.png",     // Shot of the physical prints
  challenge: "/assets/pl-challenge.png", // Graph or mobile analytics showing drop-off
  solution: "/assets/pl-solution.png",   // Shot of the new custom landing page
  features: "/assets/pl-features.png"
};
---

<Layout title="Printsloft | Project Case Study">
  <main class="case-study">
    
    <section class="cs-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-grid">
            <div class="hero-header">
                <div class="meta-tags">
                    <span>E-Commerce</span>
                    <span class="separator">•</span>
                    <span>Photography</span>
                    <span class="separator">•</span>
                    <span>D2C</span>
                </div>
                <h1>Printsloft</h1>
                <p class="hero-lead">Bringing the beauty of travel to the physical world. Validating a lean e-commerce model for the aesthetic collector.</p>
                
                <div class="tech-stack-row">
                    <span class="tech-pill">Meta Ads</span>
                    <span class="tech-pill">Custom HTML/CSS</span>
                    <span class="tech-pill">Analytics</span>
                </div>

                <a href="#" class="hero-btn">
                    View Collection <span class="btn-icon">↗</span>
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="hero-image-frame">
                <img src={images.hero} alt="Printsloft Collection" />
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats-strip">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="val">&gt;5%</span>
                    <span class="lbl">Ad CTR</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="val">₹0.94</span>
                    <span class="lbl">Cost Per Click</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="val">-50%</span>
                    <span class="lbl">Drop-off Reduced</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="val">22%</span>
                    <span class="lbl">Engagement Rate</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="story-section">
      <div class="container">
        
        <div class="chapter">
            <div class="chapter-text">
                <div class="chapter-idx">01</div>
                <h2>The Vision</h2>
                <p>As a photographer, I realized that while we capture hundreds of photos, they often remain trapped behind glass screens—viewed once and forgotten in the cloud. Printsloft was born from a desire to liberate these moments.</p>
                <p>Targeting the "Aesthetic Collector," we curate high-quality, original photography from India’s scenic destinations into premium physical prints. The brand philosophy is simple: <strong>"What your camera missed, I captured."</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="chapter-media">
                <img src={images.vision} alt="Physical Prints Showcase" /> 
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter">
            <div class="chapter-text">
                <div class="chapter-idx">02</div>
                <h2>The Leaky Bucket</h2>
                <p>The product—300 GSM matte-finish postcards—was ready, but the path to market hit a wall. We were driving high-quality traffic at an exceptionally low cost (sub-₹1 clicks), yet facing a <strong>36-73% visitor drop-off rate.</strong></p>
                <p>Data analysis revealed the bottleneck wasn't the product; it was infrastructure. Site load speeds on mobile were creating a "leaky bucket," losing customers before they could experience the brand. Furthermore, as a new entity, converting "cold" traffic immediately was a major friction point.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="chapter-media">
                <img src={images.challenge} alt="Analytics showing drop-off" />
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="chapter">
            <div class="chapter-text">
                <div class="chapter-idx">03</div>
                <h2>The Solution & Process</h2>
                <p>I approached this as a data-driven product iteration. To solve the drop-off rate, I shifted to a <strong>lean, custom-coded landing page</strong>, stripping away bloat to ensure instant loading.</p>
                <p>Strategically, I pivoted to a "Content-First" approach. Instead of forcing conversions through aggressive ads, I realized that trust cannot be bought; it must be built. We focused on storytelling to warm up the traffic before asking for the sale.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="chapter-media">
                <img src={images.solution} alt="Optimized Landing Page" />
            </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-label">Product & Strategy</h2>
        <div class="bento-grid">
            <div class="bento-item">
                <h3>Premium Build</h3>
                <p>300 GSM matte-finish paper with archival inks for longevity.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-item">
                <h3>Lean Architecture</h3>
                <p>Custom HTML/CSS landing pages designed for sub-second load times.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-item">
                <h3>Data-Driven Ads</h3>
                <p>Optimized Meta Ads targeting achieving a CPC of just ₹0.94.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-item">
                <h3>Content First</h3>
                <p>A strategy focused on storytelling and brand building over hard sales.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-item">
                <h3>Curated Collections</h3>
                <p>Original photography from Munnar, Goa, and Varkala.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-item">
                <h3>High Engagement</h3>
                <p>Creative assets maintaining a social engagement rate of over 22%.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-big-img">
            <img src={images.features} alt="Printsloft Branding" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="nav-footer">
        <a href="/" class="back-btn">Back to Home</a>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* --- LAYOUT RESET --- */
  .case-study {
    background-color: #0A0A0A;
    color: #EDEDED;
    padding-top: 6rem;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1300px; 
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  /* --- HERO --- */
  .cs-hero { margin-bottom: 4rem; }

  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 1.2fr; 
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-header { padding-right: 1rem; }

  .meta-tags {
    font-family: monospace;
    color: #B176F2;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .separator { color: #444; }

  .hero-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .hero-lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: #999;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  /* Tech Pills Style */
  .tech-stack-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  
  .tech-pill {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: #888;
    background: #111;
  }

  .hero-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background-color: #fff;
    color: #000;
    padding: 1rem 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 15px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .hero-btn:hover {
    background-color: #B176F2;
    color: #fff;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .hero-image-frame {
    width: 100%; 
    border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
    padding: 8px;
    background: #111;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }

  /* --- STATS STRIP --- */
  .stats-strip {
    border-top: 1px solid #222;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
    background: #0F0F0F;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  }

  .stat-box {
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    border-right: 1px solid #222;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-box:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .stat-box .val {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .stat-box .lbl {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #666;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* --- STORY CHAPTERS --- */
  .story-section { margin-bottom: 8rem; }

  .chapter {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 450px;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
    align-items: start; 
  }
  .chapter:last-child { border-bottom: none; margin-bottom: 0; }

  .chapter-text {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 4rem; 
    padding-right: 2rem; 
  }

  .chapter-idx {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 4px; 
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #333;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .chapter-text h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 1.2rem 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .chapter-text p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #A0A0A0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Standardized Image Container */
  .chapter-media {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    border: 1px solid #222;
    padding: 5px;
    background: #111;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .chapter-media img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* --- FEATURES BENTO --- */
  .features-section { margin-bottom: 8rem; }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .bento-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .bento-item {
    background: #111;
    border: 1px solid #222;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .bento-item:hover { border-color: #444; }

  .bento-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .bento-item p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #777;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .feature-big-img { border: 1px solid #222; }

  /* --- NAV FOOTER --- */
  .nav-footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid #222;
  }

  .back-btn {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #444;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .back-btn:hover { border-color: #B176F2; color: #B176F2; }

  /* --- MOBILE --- */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-grid, .chapter {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-image-frame { order: -1; }
    
    .chapter-media { 
        width: 100%; 
        height: auto; 
        aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    }
    .chapter-text { 
        padding-left: 0;
        padding-right: 0;
        padding-top: 1rem; 
    }
    .chapter-idx {
        position: relative; 
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        display: block;
        top: 0;
    }
    
    .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .stat-box:nth-child(2) { border-right: none; }
    .stat-box { border-bottom: 1px solid #222; }
    .stat-box:nth-last-child(-n+2) { border-bottom: none; }
  }
</style>